<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>At the temple of the goddess
while desert wind
burns through your skin
become the mirror
that reflects light
towards the heavens
where the twin sisters
claim their dominion
And remain steadfast
in the knowledge that
shifting sands
mislead only those
who ignore the stars
</code></pre></div></div>

